window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Fyodor Dostoyevsky is a titanic figure among the world's great authors, and <i>The Brothers Karamazov</i> is often hailed as his finest novel. A masterpiece on many levels, it transcends the boundaries of a gripping murder mystery to become a moving account of the battle between love and hate, faith and despair, compassion and cruelty, good and evil.</p>"; 
